{
  "stem": "25114.7",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's going to belong to White Russia-- Belarus-- to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, since the Soviet Union was still, in '44-- in the year '44-- allied with America and the West, so, as I said, the Polish-- and there was a Polish government already established in Poland, in a certain part of Poland, which was free-- like, in Lublin.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, as I said, the Polish citizens who prefer to be Polish citizens rather than Soviet citizens have the right to repatriation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took this opportunity to go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which wasn't yet established, and there wasn't an army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we can see what we can do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there, he had to go to the army, and everything-- everything was finishing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody who went to the army didn't return, because they send them right to the first front-- first fire and all of that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the partisans that came out of the-- of the forests, that survived all the Holocaust and everything, and went to the armies-- they were all killed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of our-- of our group was killed who came-- who escaped with us, left a son.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Asael got killed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went into the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He got killed in a battle right after the liberation, one of the Bielski brothers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all--thing--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tried to somehow-- by-- by our wits, we tried to get out of getting-- going into the army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we choose this loophole, and went to the thing-- to the-- whatever the authority was they established for this-- for this district-- the high authority.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, we are Polish citizens, and we want to stay Polish citizens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we want to be repatriated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we did it-- got accepted.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
